sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Envoy Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant BBR as Body-Based Router<br/>9004/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant EPP as Endpoint Picker<br/>9002/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelPod as Model Server Pod<br/>varies/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,ModelPod: Flow 1: Inference Request with Body-Based Routing

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / API Key

    Gateway->>BBR: ext-proc request (body)<br/>gRPC/9004, TLS (self-signed)
    BBR->>K8sAPI: Watch ConfigMaps (bbr-managed)<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>BBR: Adapter→Base model mappings
    BBR-->>Gateway: ext-proc response<br/>Inject: X-Gateway-Model-Name header

    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc request (headers + body)<br/>gRPC/9002, TLS (self-signed)

    Note over EPP: Scheduling Pipeline:<br/>1. Filter (prefix cache, SLO headroom)<br/>2. Score (KV cache, queue depth, LoRA affinity)<br/>3. Pick (max score / weighted random)

    EPP-->>Gateway: ext-proc response<br/>Set: target endpoint address

    Gateway->>ModelPod: Forward inference request<br/>HTTP/varies, per-gateway config
    ModelPod-->>Gateway: Inference response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Client,ModelPod: Flow 2: Model Server Metrics Scraping (Background)

    loop Every 50ms (configurable)
        EPP->>ModelPod: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, InsecureSkipVerify=true
        ModelPod-->>EPP: Prometheus metrics<br/>(KV cache util, queue depth,<br/>running requests, LoRA status)
        Note over EPP: Update in-memory datastore<br/>for scheduling decisions
    end

    Note over Client,ModelPod: Flow 3: CRD Watches (Background)

    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool, InferenceObjective,<br/>InferenceModelRewrite, Pods<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>EPP: CRD/Pod change events
    Note over EPP: Update pool config,<br/>endpoint registry,<br/>model rewrite rules

    Note over Client,ModelPod: Flow 4: Latency Prediction (Optional)

    opt Latency Predictor Enabled
        EPP->>EPP: Collect request telemetry
        Note right of EPP: Training Server (sidecar)<br/>HTTP/8000
        Note right of EPP: Prediction Server (sidecar)<br/>HTTP/8001+
    end

    Note over Client,ModelPod: Flow 5: Observability (Optional)

    opt Tracing Enabled
        EPP-->>EPP: Export traces<br/>gRPC/4317 → OTLP Collector
    end
